-Yes.

00:46:27.340 --> 00:46:27.705
In her dressing room--

00:46:27.705 --> 00:46:28.800
-In her dressing room?

00:46:28.800 --> 00:46:29.300
-Backstage?

00:46:29.300 --> 00:46:31.820
-Yes.

