00:46:55.534 --> 00:46:57.200
DAVID THORBURN: I
hope you're picking up

00:46:57.200 --> 00:46:59.530
the subtext that these
old men are revealing.

00:47:03.450 --> 00:47:05.476
-It's getting a
bit late gentlemen.

00:47:05.476 --> 00:47:07.408
Perhaps we had
better get to bed.

00:47:16.585 --> 00:47:18.340
-Someday I'll tell
you my experiences

00:47:18.340 --> 00:47:20.340
with a young actress
named Lillian Russel.

00:47:20.340 --> 00:47:22.010
-Did you know her?

00:47:22.010 --> 00:47:24.146
-I stood in the snow
four hours to get--

00:47:24.146 --> 00:47:26.470
-Is that our doorbell?

