00:48:17.412 --> 00:48:18.370
and Seven Dwarfs scene.

00:48:21.660 --> 00:48:22.760
-Those are my colleagues.

00:48:22.760 --> 00:48:24.200
-Oh!

00:48:24.200 --> 00:48:26.140
-I must apologize for
their lack of costume.

00:48:26.140 --> 00:48:28.680
-Oh, that's all right professor.

00:48:28.680 --> 00:48:29.990
-I haven't got my tie on.

00:48:29.990 --> 00:48:34.840
-Oh, you know once I watched
my big brother shave.

00:48:34.840 --> 00:48:36.146
-Would you come in?

