-Well, I got thinking
it over, and I

00:48:44.555 --> 00:48:46.680
said to myself, who am I
to give science the brush?

00:48:46.680 --> 00:48:48.255
-And I take it
you've reconsidered?

00:48:48.255 --> 00:48:49.380
-Yeah, that's the big idea.

00:48:52.747 --> 00:48:54.671
-Oh dear, oh dear.

00:48:54.671 --> 00:48:57.570
-Look out.

00:48:57.570 --> 00:48:59.180
-That was Professor Oddly.

00:48:59.180 --> 00:49:00.920
-Anymore of them around?

00:49:00.920 --> 00:49:03.170
-I hope not.

00:49:03.170 --> 00:49:05.080
-Hey, who decorated this place?

00:49:05.080 --> 00:49:07.470
The mug that shot Lincoln?

00:49:07.470 --> 00:49:09.040
-This is our work room.

00:49:09.040 --> 00:49:11.290
The living quarters
are upstairs.

00:49:11.290 --> 00:49:12.870
-Whee, that's a lot of books.

00:49:12.870 --> 00:49:14.010
All of them different?

00:49:14.010 --> 00:49:15.680
-I trust.

00:49:15.680 --> 00:49:16.660
May I have your coat?

00:49:16.660 --> 00:49:17.400
-Yeah, thanks.

00:49:23.510 --> 00:49:24.460
Oh, Greek philosophy.

00:49:24.460 --> 00:49:27.660
I've got a set like this
with a radio inside.

00:49:27.660 --> 00:49:29.430
-Are you sure you
don't want your coat?

