00:50:42.450 --> 00:50:44.500
-If you want me tomorrow
morning at 9:30--

00:50:44.500 --> 00:50:46.330
-Oh, I do Ms. O'Shea.

00:50:46.330 --> 00:50:53.860
But even the most free-thinking
people must respect the--

